Titolo: An American Tail: The Computer Adventures of Fievel and His Friends

Anno: 1993

Descrizione: An American Tail: The Computer Adventures of Fievel and His Friends is a 1993 point-and-click adventure game by Capstone Software and Manley & Associates, Inc for DOS, based on both of the first two movies, An American Tail and An American Tail: Fievel Goes West. The game's manual included a glossary to define difficult words for younger players. In 1994 the game was released with Trolls and Rock-A-Doodle Computerized Coloring Book on the Capstone CD Game Kids Collection.

Genere: Adventure 

Valutazione: N/A
